Subject: EPP - Upload speed issues
Description:
Hello! We have had several issues with upload speed reported by several employees after we activated Content Aware Protection Policies in EndPoint Protector, with a blocklist for personal emails and shared drives.
Could you please clarify if this could be a result of this blocklist, and what we can do to resolve it?
Thank you very much.
Solution_Comment__c: Enabled Intercept VPN and the upload speed returned to normal.
